Content regulation
Content Policy
Generalization of terminology
2.1
2.1. You may not post any of the following content to SimSimi(through the publishing feature, such as teaching).
You can not post the following content to the service: All the expressions you generate using text and other media are content (Conversation, Talk, Teach, Name, Interest, Characteristic, etc.). In the service, "generate" is considered the same as "post".
Defining the concepts of "content" and "post" specifically and clearly
2.2
Content that violates these prohibitions may be removed mechanically within the Service by the removal rules. If reported separately to us, the content will be removed by our internal review.
The content that violated this policy can be mechanically or manually deleted or blocked by multiple rules, such as report and monitoring within a service. Violation levels affect your service permissions.
Clarification
